    "RP 33due to Z 2 -valued cohomology group.",
    "Hence, the angular momentum of this wrappedJHEP12(2024)227D3-brane is denoted by lN, with l = 0 for the Z 2 -even generator, and l = 1 for the Z 2 -odd generator.",
    "Hence the energy and angular momentum of the configuration are∆ = J = 2mN + 2 n≥0 a -n a n -2 j≥0 b -j b j + lN, (4.61)where l is 0 or 1.",
    "The index computed from the gravitational data (4.61) takes the form I See[27] for the analysis of the giant graviton expansions of the half-indices of unitary gauge theories.",
    "More generally, one can find dual descriptions of corner configurations from the junctions of 5-branes preserving N = (0, 4) supersymmetry[11][12][13]."
